///
/// Resolves both endpoints to commit ids and compares them via two
/// revset-ancestry probes (`a::b`, `b::a`). When the remote bookmark
/// does not resolve, returns `NoRemote` — the caller's action phase
/// treats that as a no-op (and prints a skip line).
fn classify(
